{
  "experiment_id": "sp500_8020_v1",
  "schema_version": "1.0",
  "description": "Full S&P 500 IQN 25k scale-up with chronological train/eval split (train 2016-01-01 -> 2023-12-31, eval 2024-01-01 -> 2026-05-26). Split date 2024-01-01 matches the successful 25k run and the DEMO10 baseline (clean_25k_baseline_v1.json) for direct comparability. Multi-regime eval window chosen to avoid the single-bull-quarter BUY-collapse seen in the earlier 2026-Q1 eval. Mirrors clean_25k_baseline_v1.json hyperparameters (stockdss_long_v1, LayerNorm on, q50 scoring). All experiment-defining values are explicit here; .env must NOT override any of these.",
  "dataset": {
    "dataset_id": "sp500",
    "pit_split_id": "sp500_pit_2024",
    "universe_id": "sp500",
    "frozen_market_file": "data/market/daily/imports/market_data_full_500.csv",
    "tickers": "ALL_SP500",
    "train_start": "2016-01-01",
    "train_end": "2023-12-31",
    "eval_start": "2024-01-01",
    "eval_end": "2026-05-26",
    "note": "Frozen CSV (market_data_full_500.csv, 467 tickers, 2566 rows/ticker). No live download. Chronological split at 2024-01-01 (matches the successful run and DEMO10). tickers=ALL_SP500 means the full universe is read from the frozen file; the explicit ticker list is not pinned here because it is the entire S&P 500 as present in the frozen file."
  },
